ActNunavut Act
SubjectAdministration and Control of Certain Public Lands in the Nunavut ** Transfer **
PrecisOrder authorizing the TRANSFER TO THE COMMISSIONER OF NUNAVUT, in perpetuity, the administration and control of the surface interest of an un-surveyed parcel of land comprising approximately 2902.5 hectares, located near to and west of IQALUIT, Nunavut, in order to allow the Territorial Government to administer these lands for the purpose of expanding the Sylvia Grinnell Territorial Park.
RegistrationRegistration: UNR/
